    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You take a moment to catch your breath and refocus.</p><p><em><strong>Range:</strong> Self</em></p><p>Make a DC 10 Martial Check.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> You gain 1 Temp HP for 1 Round.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> You gain 2 Temp HP for 1 Round.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success (each 5):</strong> +1 Temp HP.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Temp HP will not be removed automatically after 1 Round.</em></p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Maneuver Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Increased Temp HP: (1 SP) </strong>You gain +2 Temp HP.</p><p><strong>Physical Resolve: (1 SP)</strong> You gain ADV on Physical Saves for the duration.</p><p><strong>Mental Resolve: (1 SP)</strong> You gain ADV on Mental Saves for the duration.</p>",
